com.bhaptics.ble.service

Class BaseGattCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.bluetooth.BluetoothGattCallback
      • com.bhaptics.ble.service.BaseGattCallback

  • public class BaseGattCallback
extends android.bluetooth.BluetoothGattCallback
    GattCallbacks from BLE devices.

    Connect/disconnect and read/write operations from devices return their callbacks to this.

    It just relays their callbacks to BaseClient
